caption:
You know that moment when you almost got there?

When your opponent burns by you.
When your teammate passed into space, but your legs didn't move.
When your body hesitated for half a second too long.

That’s speed.
That’s what’s missing.
And you feel it every time it costs you.

This is what separates the athletes who talk about it from the ones who show it.

DM us or comment "FAST" if you’re ready to get serious about your speed.

I’ll send over our full Speed & Acceleration Session + discuss our 1-on-1 Coaching so you don’t have to figure it out alone.
